OL,3,CSenedd Member banned from Welsh
OL,4,CParliament over racial slur
OL,6,FA member of the Senedd will be
OL,7,Fsuspended for two weeks because of
OL,8,Fcomments that she made in a private
OL,9,FWhatsApp group which included a racial
OL,10,Fslur.
OL,12,FFellow MSs voted to back the
OL,13,Frecommendations of the Standards
OL,14,FCommittee that Laura Anne Jones be
OL,15,Fsuspended without pay for 14 days
OL,16,Fbecause she was found to have breached
OL,17,Fthe Senedd's code of conduct.
