OL,6,FMs Jones is now Reform UK's only
OL,7,Fmember of the Welsh Parliament but had
OL,8,Fpreviously sat as a Conservative
OL,9,Fmember.
OL,11,FIn an emotional speech to the Senedd,
OL,12,FMs Jones repeated her apology and said
OL,13,Fshe accepted the findings of the
OL,14,FStandards Commissioners report into
OL,15,Fthe allegations against her.
