OL,6,FShe welcomed the decision to clear her
OL,7,Fof allegations of expenses fraud but
OL,8,Fcriticised both the length of time the
OL,9,Fprocess had taken - two years - and
OL,10,Fwhat she called 'continuous leaks to
OL,11,Fthe press' which led to a 'significant
OL,12,Ftoll' on her own mental health and
OL,13,Fthat of her children.
OL,15,FThe Senedd's Standards Committee
OL,16,Frecommended the suspension following a
OL,17,Freport by the Standards Commissioner
OL,18,Finto three allegations.
