OL,6,FThe Commissioner's report found that
OL,7,Fshe had breached the code of conduct
OL,8,Fin two instances, one in which she
OL,9,Fused a slur about Chinese people in a
OL,10,Fprivate Whatsapp group chat in August
OL,11,F2023 and another in which she failed
OL,12,Fto act against comments made by a
OL,13,Fstaff member in another WhatsApp group.
OL,15,FShe was cleared of a third allegation
OL,16,Fthat had fraudulently made false
OL,17,Fexpenses claims. The Commissioner
OL,18,Ffound there had been "no breach of the
OL,19,Fcode of conduct" in relation to that.
