OL,6,FSpeaking in the Senedd tonight
OL,7,F(Wednesday November 19th), Ms Jones
OL,8,Fbecame visibly emotional as she
OL,9,Fdetailed the "hugely detrimental
OL,10,Fimpact" on her health and wellbeing as
OL,11,Fa result of the two year investigation.
OL,13,FShe said she accepted the
OL,14,Fcommissioners findings in the report,
OL,15,Fwelcomed the finding of no fraudulent
OL,16,Factivity, and also apologied for the
OL,17,F"regrettable" language used in the
OL,18,Fmessages.
