OL,6,FShe went on to add, "I have reflected
OL,7,Fdeeply on this and I wholly accept the
OL,8,Fneed to take greater care with my
OL,9,Flanguage at all times. I also want to
OL,10,Fsay how harrowing this nearly two year
OL,11,Finvestigation has been.
OL,13,F"I'm not afraid to put on record that
OL,14,Fthis process, and the continuous leaks
OL,15,Fto the press, particularly trying to
OL,16,Fframe me for a serious crime stemming
OL,17,Ffrom this clearly malicious attempt to
OL,18,Fdiscredit me has had a negative impact
OL,19,Fon my family, especially my children
OL,20,Fas well as a hugely detrimental impact
OL,21,Fon my own health and mental health.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
