OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F469A1763749543
OL,3,CSenedd Member banned from Welsh
OL,4,CParliament over racial slur
OL,6,F"The pressure of being portrayed in
OL,7,Fsuch a serious and distressing way,
OL,8,Fdespite the clear findings that it was
OL,9,Fno wrongdoing, has taken a significant
OL,10,Ftoll on me, which led me to try and
OL,11,Ftry drown out that noise and nearly
OL,12,Ftake my own life a number of times.
OL,14,F"I wouldn't wish this of what I've had
OL,15,Fto experience on my worst enemy, and I
OL,16,Fhope for your sakes that this doesn't
OL,17,Fhappen to any of you.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
