OL,6,F"So I will now try to turn this awful
OL,7,Fexperience into a positive one, and
OL,8,FI'll be campaigning hard to try and
OL,9,Fmake positive changes to the system to
OL,10,Fbetter protect members centred around
OL,11,Fmembers being innocent until proven
OL,12,Fguilty, the foundation of which our
OL,13,Fcountry is founded on, getting the
OL,14,Fsupport they need and helping to
OL,15,Fimprove the process.
