OL,6,F"I will say, it does concern me that
OL,7,Fthe committee, made up of Labour,
OL,8,FPlaid and Tory were allowed to add on
OL,9,Fto the end of factual, thorough,
OL,10,Fnearly two year investigation with
OL,11,Fsome non facts and speculation,
OL,12,Fhearsay.
OL,14,F"Arguably this shows that perhaps, as
OL,15,Fother members have argued, that this
OL,16,Fpart of the process isn't ideal and
OL,17,Fcould bring into question
OL,18,Fimpartiality, which is perhaps a
OL,19,Fstrong argument for a truly
OL,20,Findependent process going forward into
OL,21,Fthe next Senedd.
