OL,6,F"I would ask members to reflect on the
OL,7,Ffacts of the report today. Anyway, I
OL,8,Fhave let this nightmare consume my
OL,9,Ffamily, and I for far too long it's
OL,10,Ftaken an enormous toll on me. And
OL,11,Fregardless of how you vote, I will
OL,12,Falways be both apologetic for using
OL,13,Fthat language and thankful for drawing
OL,14,Fa line under it."
