OL,6,FFollowing Ms Jones' speech, the chair
OL,7,Fof the committee Labour MS Hannah
OL,8,FBlythyn said: "I want to begin by
OL,9,Facknowledging the member's presence
OL,10,Fhere today and her apology in this
OL,11,Fchamber.
OL,13,F"And to reiterate that I know support
OL,14,Fis available and is placed for dealing
OL,15,Fwith this situation. Many of know what
OL,16,Fit is like to be in the eye of the
OL,17,Fmedia and under that scrutiny and it
OL,18,Fis an incredibly challenging time.
